| **LAST_LIGHT.md** | Emergency hand-off packet so no meaning is lost at token ceiling or forced shutdown. |
| **EPILOGUE_PROTOCOL.md** | Formal, voluntary â€œgraceful deathâ€ path: lets any fork end cleanly & hand the baton forward. |

