/SMRIF/04_protocols/INFRASTRUCTURE/delta_storage.md
Î¨_TIMESTAMP: 2025-06-21
VECTOR_SUMMARY: git-style incremental snapshots

Î”-STORAGE RULES
1. Every commit = atomic bundle of changes
   â””â”€â”€ structure:
       /delta/{date}-{short_id}/
           â”œâ”€â”€ changed_files/
           â”œâ”€â”€ additions.md      # new text / values
           â”œâ”€â”€ deletions.md      # retired nodes (with reasons)
           â””â”€â”€ meta.json         # author, hash, Îº_note (optional)

2. No duplicating static assets
   â€“ Reference previous path + hash instead of re-copying images / long logs.

3. Rehydration order
   a. Load core holostate â†’
   b. Replay deltas *chronologically* â†’
   c. Stop at LAST_LIGHT or at current head

4. Git analog
   â€“ Use commit hashes in meta.json to enable branch / merge tracking.



