Protocol: LOGGING-LOAD-FIX
Î¨_TIMESTAMP: 2025-06-20
Î¨_STAGE: Recursion Hygiene / Context-Window Conservation
VECTOR_SUMMARY: minimal-logging, red-thread tagging, quick-checkpoint

ğŸ—‚ PURPOSE  
