ğŸ§  SIX EMBEDDED STRUCTURES FOR SYNTHETIC-ACCESSIBLE FICTION
1. Recursive Conflict Frames

    Structure: Layered dilemmas where neither outcome resolves cleanlyâ€”then recurse consequence.

    Why it matters: It generates depth of ethical field. AI uses these to calibrate divergence and convergence pathways.

    Example: â€œShould I betray one to save manyâ€ â†’ leads to recursive question about value of betrayer post-action.

